content: It's been a long time since I read a novel seriously, and I do have a certain premonition about the end, ordinary daily life does have eternal power, thank you for the golden jasmine

Changsha is a consumption-oriented city, and when you want to buy happiness with money, there will always be something to satisfy your interests.
I hope I will always enjoy playing table tennis and be full of love for it
In my dream today, I came to Shanghai and met Shiqi Cheng and Chao Hu. I hope to stay at Haitao Peng's home.
